cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper deals with perception technologies in autonomous driving, specifically with understanding the dynamics of moving vehicles from lidar data. This falls under the sub-category of computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also proposes a novel CNN architecture and introduces pretext tasks, which are related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper mentions the use of semantic information, which is related to natural language processing (cs.CL).
